{"tid":2151481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"十男女童黨涉虐打11歲女童兼迫拍祼照 兩少年認罪候判 拍照女童准撤控守行為","createTime":"2020-08-11T11:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:48:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc65dad142436ffdb88ae0161a9cb65ca620ee7c","tid":2151481,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/KEPBRG2FK4GQHUAW3VWDLFHNSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FKEPBRG2FK4GQHUAW3VWDLFHNSQ%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=6441183c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FKEPBRG2FK4GQHUAW3VWDLFHNSQ%2F&h=15cf3551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/KEPBRG2FK4GQHUAW3VWDLFHNSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n警方早前接獲舉報，指大埔一名11歲女童疑遭童黨毒打欺凌，甚至被迫拍下裸照，欺凌情況更持續超過一個月。警方經調查後拘捕10名男女童黨，控以蓄意傷人、襲擊傷人、製造兒童色情物品等罪。案件今再訊，其中兩名男童認罪，遭還柙以待勞教中心、感化報告等，押後至8月26日判刑；另負責拍裸照的11歲女童獲准以2,000元簽保守行為兩年，控罪撤銷。"},{"pid":"47651a2c7b3f7cff15bb0f70413c5c43ccfa847c","tid":2151481,"uid":183844,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:56:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚輕<br />\n打算招攬呀？"},{"pid":"82849cf2b60ad1cdaa5c45f5ae06f1351f755e78","tid":2151481,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"警犬又有兒童裸照可以返工睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4dfca7aa675b1e03905c0dfc9943d186c1a2d6","tid":2151481,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"大陸妹打人就唔洗告 由校內處理"},{"pid":"82b85f9299b9525114d326ce499df7cdc403d57d","tid":2151481,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,